                            <comment id="18504" author="robh" created="Mon, 10 Jul 2006 21:59:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Paul,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen changed this to increase consistency across the codebase, but I agree that this particular method should retain public access, so I have restored it in CVS.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Rob&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
